WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL 28 SEP BY
   M/V RAMFORM VANGUARD TOWING 12
   7000 METER CABLES ALONG TRACKLINES BETWEEN:
   A. 35-28.12S 053-17.98W AND 36-47.97S 052-07.70W,
   B. 36-44.40S 052-01.73W AND 35-43.63S 052-57.87W.
   NINE MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 29 SEP 13.
